messages.messageBody:
Hi all,

Well, I finally have a *new* computer and am back on line! I have soooo much
to tell everyone, but so much to catch on (I lost EVERYTHING when my power
supply blew...it took EVERYTHING w/it including the motherboard and hard drive.
There was no saving the old one). Anyway, I do have so much WONDERFUL NEWS
to share about my daughter & the great things she is doing & what she gets to
do. But, I need to do it in another e-mail (hopefully in the morning) as I'm
really tired. BUT, I promise to share w/all, as this mom just can't keep it in
anymore!

Take Care, & can't wait to chat w/you all soon!

Tracy


[Non-text portions of this message have been removed]
